General.Name: Prosense.tv
General.Description:
Prosense.tv is a working business with an already existing functional platform for filming, transporting and viewing professional VR broadcasts.

Prosense.tv transforms the technology of centralized content delivery into a global decentralized peer-to-peer ProsenseLive platform with a payment collection system in which intellectual property rights are protected by blockchain cryptography and all transactions are confidential.

ICO.Description:
Prosense.tv is a working business with an already existing functional platform for filming, transporting and viewing professional VR broadcasts.

Prosense.tv transforms the technology of centralized content delivery into a global decentralized peer-to-peer ProsenseLive platform with a payment collection system in which intellectual property rights are protected by blockchain cryptography and all transactions are confidential.

Team:

  • Stanislav Glukhoedov: CEO and Co-founder. 
  • Vladimir Bakuteev: Co-founder. 
  • Grigory Vasinkevic: Co-founder. 
  • Nataliya Kopylova: Co-founder. 

Prior to the ICO, Prosense.tv will be holding a pre-ICO from the 19th of October, 2017 to the 15th of November, 2017. The pre-ICO funding cap is $10,000,000 and the minimum entry threshold is $20,000.

Pre-ICO bonus: 19th of October to 1st of November - 25% discount; 2nd to 8th of November - 20% discount; 9th to 15th of November - 15% discount.

After the pre-ICO, Prosense.tv will be holding its ICO on the 16th of November, 2017. The ICO funding cap is 30,000,000 USD and the minimum entry threshold is $50. The ICO is expected to end on the 16th of December, 2017 or when the funding cap is reached.

ICO Bonus: 16th of November - Whitelist only. Bonus 10%; 17th to 22nd of November - Bonus 5%; 3 weeks of ICO 0%.
